data.description: Beautiful home on approximately a half acre lot just outside city limits. Large front and back porches with beautiful railings.  The back porch is covered allowing for an additional living space. This home includes features like:  a split bedroom floor plan, an abundance of storage and open concept living and kitchen area.   Large kitchen with several work spaces for multiple cooks at once.  A large Master Suite includes a garden tub, separate shower as well as separate vanities. Backyard storage building with a loft that is insulated and has power.
